Layout
  - default html template
  - home page/controller
  - errors/404

Application
  - Base Controller

Restaurants
  - development database/config
  - restaurants schema/table: id, name, created (UTC), updated (UTC)
  - restaurants model (abstracted from ORM)
  - restaurants controller: index/view
  - restaurants views: index/view
  - restaurants/restaurant partials/elements for index
  - html encoding
  - menu/route based links
  - 404 restaurant not found by number and when not int
  
Authentication Part I
  - users schema/table: id, emailAddress, password, recoveryToken, confirmed, created (UTC), updated (UTC)
  - users model
	or
  - built-in framework authentication/membership if available
  - account controller: login, logout, register
  - login form partial
  - register form partial
  - login, logout, register views

Authentication Part II
  - password recovery
  - password change
  - account controller: reset, change
  - reset/change partials
  - reset/change views
